               <head>Sharh-i Masnavi</head>
               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of Sharḥ-i Mas̲navī</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2008112367 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2006003807" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_1053-item1">
                     <title xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="work_22198">Sharḥ-i Mas̲navī</title>
                     <title xml:lang="per" key="work_22198">شرح مثنوى</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="per">Persian</textLang>
                     <note>
                        <p>The text of the <title>Mas̲navī-'i maʿnavī</title> of <persName key="viaf_98930150" role="aut">Jalāl al-Dīn Rūmī</persName> (d. 670/1271) together together with brief comments on selected passages by an unnamed author.
                        </p>
                        <p>Incomplete at beginning and end</p>
                        <p>Contents: Daftar 2 (f. 49r); dafter 3 (f. 72v); daftar 4 (f. 96v); daftar 5 (f. 115v); daftar 6 (f. 139v). </p>
                        <p>nīm-shikastah; 21 lines per page.</p>
                        <p>Dates given in the colophons vary from 5 Sha’ban regnal year 46 of ʻĀlamgīr to 5 Shavval regnal year 47 (1703-1705).</p>
                     </note>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="viaf_98930150">Jalāl al-Dīn Rūmī</persName>
                     </author>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
